quran[137]{c,v,t}:
  58,1,KAD SEMI’ALLAHU KAWLEL-LETI TUXHADILUKE FI ZEWXHIHA WE TESHTEKI ‘ILA ELLAHI WEL-LAHU JESMA’U TEHAWUREKUMA ‘INNALL-LLAHE SEMI’UN BESIRUN
  58,2,EL-LEDHINE JUDHAHIRUNE MINKUM MIN NISA’IHIM MA HUNNE ‘UMMEHATIHIM ‘IN ‘UMMEHATUHUM ‘ILLAL-LA’I WELEDNEHUM WE ‘INNEHUM LEJEKULUNE MUNKERÆN MINEL-KAWLI WE ZURÆN WE ‘INNALL-LLAHE LE’AFUWUN GAFURUN
  58,3,WEL-LEDHINE JUDHAHIRUNE MIN NISA’IHIM THUMME JA’UDUNE LIMA KALU FETEHRIRU REKABETIN MIN KABLI ‘EN JETEMASSA DHALIKUM TU’ADHUNE BIHI WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE HABIRUN
  58,4,FEMEN LEM JEXHID FESIJAMU SHEHREJNI MUTETABI’AJNI MIN KABLI ‘EN JETEMASSA FEMEN LEM JESTETI’ FE’IT’AMU SITTINE MISKINÆN DHALIKE LITU’UMINU BILLAHI WE RESULIHI WE TILKE HUDUDU ELLAHI WE LILKAFIRINE ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  58,5,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JUHADDUNEL-LAHE WE RESULEHU KUBITU KEMA KUBITEL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM WE KAD ‘ENZELNA ‘AJATIN BEJJINATIN WE LILKAFIRINE ‘ADHABUN MUHINUN
  58,6,JEWME JEB’ATHUHUMU ELLAHU XHEMI’ÆN FEJUNEBBI’UHUM BIMA ‘AMILU ‘EHSAHU ELLAHU WE NESUHU WEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN SHEHIDUN
  58,7,‘ELEM TERA ‘ENNEL-LAHE JA’LEMU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI MA JEKUNU MIN NEXHWA THELATHETIN ‘ILLA HUWE RABI’UHUM WE LA HAMSETIN ‘ILLA HUWE SADISUHUM WE LA ‘EDNA MIN DHALIKE WE LA ‘EKTHERE ‘ILLA HUWE ME’AHUM ‘EJNE MA KANU THUMME JUNEBBI’UHUM BIMA ‘AM
  58,8,‘ELEM TERA ‘ILAL-LEDHINE NUHU ‘ANI EN-NEXHWA THUMME JA’UDUNE LIMA NUHU ‘ANHU WE JETENAXHEWNE BIL-’ITHMI WEL-’UDWANI WE MA’SIJETI ER-RESULI WE ‘IDHA XHA’UKE HEJJEWKE BIMA LEM JUHEJJIKE BIHI ELLAHU WE JEKULUNE FI ‘ENFUSIHIM LEWLA JU’ADHDHIBUNALLAHU BIMA NEK
  58,9,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA TENAXHEJTUM FELA TETENAXHEW BIL-’ITHMI WEL-’UDWANI WE MA’SIJETI ER-RESULI WE TENAXHEW BIL-BIRRI WET-TEKWA WE ETTEKU ELLAHEL-LEDHI ‘ILEJHI TUHSHERUNE
  58,10,‘INNEMA EN-NEXHWA MINE ESH-SHEJTANI LIJEHZUNEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE LEJSE BIDARRIHIM SHEJ’ÆN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE ‘ALA ELLAHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MU’UMINUNE
  58,11,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA KILE LEKUM TEFESSEHU FIL-MEXHALISI FAFSEHU JEFSEHI ELLAHU LEKUM WE ‘IDHA KILE ENSHUZU FANSHUZU JERFA’I ELLAHUL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU MINKUM WEL-LEDHINE ‘UTUL-’ILME DEREXHATIN WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE HABIRUN
  58,12,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA NAXHEJTUMU ER-RESULE FEKADDIMU BEJNE JEDEJ NEXHWAKUM SEDEKATEN DHALIKE HAJRUN LEKUM WE ‘ETHERU FE’IN LEM TEXHIDU FE’INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  58,13,‘E’ESHFEKTUM ‘EN TUKADDIMU BEJNE JEDEJ NEXHWAKUM SEDEKATIN FE’IDH LEM TEF’ALU WE TABEL-LAHU ‘ALEJKUM FE’EKIMU ES-SELÆTE WE ‘ATU EZ-ZEKÆTE WE ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE RESULEHU WEL-LAHU HABIRUN BIMA TA’MELUNE
  58,14,‘ELEM TERA ‘ILAL-LEDHINE TEWELLEW KAWMÆN GADIBEL-LAHU ‘ALEJHIM MA HUM MINKUM WE LA MINHUM WE JEHLIFUNE ‘ALEL-KEDHIBI WE HUM JA’LEMUNE
  58,15,‘E’ADDEL-LAHU LEHUM ‘ADHABÆN SHEDIDÆN ‘INNEHUM SA’E MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  58,16,ETTEHADHU ‘EJMANEHUM XHUNNETEN FESEDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI FELEHUM ‘ADHABUN MUHINUN
  58,17,LEN TUGNIJE ‘ANHUM ‘EMWALUHUM WE LA ‘EWLADUHUM MINEL-LAHI SHEJ’ÆN ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HUM FIHA HALIDUNE
  58,18,JEWME JEB’ATHUHUMU ELLAHU XHEMI’ÆN FEJEHLIFUNE LEHU KEMA JEHLIFUNE LEKUM WE JEHSEBUNE ‘ENNEHUM ‘ALA SHEJ’IN ‘ELA ‘INNEHUM HUMUL-KADHIBUNE
  58,19,ESTEHWEDHE ‘ALEJHIMU ESH-SHEJTANU FE’ENSAHUM DHIKREL-LAHI ‘ULA’IKE HIZBU ESH-SHEJTANI ‘ELA ‘INNE HIZBE ESH-SHEJTANI HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  58,20,‘INNEL-LEDHINE JUHADDUNEL-LAHE WE RESULEHU ‘ULA’IKE FIL-’EDHELLINE
  58,21,KETEBEL-LAHU LE’EGLIBENNE ‘ENA WE RUSULI ‘INNALL-LLAHE KAWIJUN ‘AZIZUN
  58,22,LA TEXHIDU KAWMÆN JU’UMINUNE BILLAHI WEL-JEWMIL-’AHIRI JUWADDUNE MEN HADDEL-LAHE WE RESULEHU WE LEW KANU ‘ABA’EHUM ‘EW ‘EBNA’EHUM ‘EW ‘IHWANEHUM ‘EW ‘ASHIRETEHUM ‘ULA’IKE KETEBE FI KULUBIHIMUL-’IMANE WE ‘EJJEDEHUM BIRUHIN MINHU WE JUDHILUHUM XHENNATIN TEX
  59,1,SEBBEHE LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  59,2,HUWEL-LEDHI ‘EHREXHEL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN ‘EHLIL-KITABI MIN DIJARIHIM LI’WWELIL-HESHRI MA DHENENTUM ‘EN JEHRUXHU WE DHENNU ‘ENNEHUM MANI’ATUHUM HUSUNUHUM MINEL-LAHI FE’ETAHUMU ELLAHU MIN HEJTHU LEM JEHTESIBU WE KADHEFE FI KULUBIHIMU ER-RU’BE JUHRIBUNE BUJU
  59,3,WE LEWLA ‘EN KETEBEL-LAHU ‘ALEJHIMUL-XHELA’E LE’ADHDHEBEHUM FI ED-DUNJA WE LEHUM FIL-’AHIRETI ‘ADHABU EN-NARI
  59,4,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM SHAKKU ELLAHE WE RESULEHU WE MEN JUSHAKKI ELLAHE FE’INNALL-LLAHE SHEDIDUL-’IKABI
  59,5,MA KATA’TUM MIN LINETIN ‘EW TEREKTUMUHA KA’IMETEN ‘ALA ‘USULIHA FEBI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE LIJUHZIJEL-FASIKINE
  59,6,WE MA ‘EFA’EL-LAHU ‘ALA RESULIHI MINHUM FEMA ‘EWXHEFTUM ‘ALEJHI MIN HAJLIN WE LA RIKABIN WE LEKINNALL-LLAHE JUSELLITU RUSULEHU ‘ALA MEN JESHA’U WEL-LAHU ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  59,7,MA ‘EFA’EL-LAHU ‘ALA RESULIHI MIN ‘EHLIL-KURA FELILLAHI WE LILRRESULI WE LIDHIL-KURBA WEL-JETAMA WEL-MESAKINI WE EBNI ES-SEBILI KEJ LA JEKUNE DULETEN BEJNEL-’EGNIJA’I MINKUM WE MA ‘ATAKUMU ER-RESULU FEHUDHUHU WE MA NEHAKUM ‘ANHU FANTEHU WE ETTEKU ELLAHE ‘
  59,8,LILFUKARA’IL-MUHAXHIRINEL-LEDHINE ‘UHRIXHU MIN DIARIHIM WE ‘EMWALIHIM JEBTEGUNE FEDLÆN MINEL-LAHI WE RIDWANÆN WE JENSURUNEL-LAHE WE RESULEHU ‘ULA’IKE HUMU ES-SADIKUNE
  59,9,WEL-LEDHINE TEBEWWE’U ED-DARE WEL-’IMANE MIN KABLIHIM JUHIBBUNE MEN HAXHERE ‘ILEJHIM WE LA JEXHIDUNE FI SUDURIHIM HAXHETEN MIMMA ‘UTU WE JU’UTHIRUNE ‘ALA ‘ENFUSIHIM WE LEW KANE BIHIM HASASETUN WE MEN JUKA SHUHHE NEFSIHI FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-MUFLIHUNE
  59,10,WEL-LEDHINE XHA’U MIN BA’DIHIM JEKULUNE REBBENA EGFIR LENA WE LI’EHWANINAL-LEDHINE SEBEKUNA BIL-’IMANI WE LA TEXH’AL FI KULUBINA GILLÆN LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU REBBENA ‘INNEKE RE’UFUN REHIMUN
  59,11,‘ELEM TERA ‘ILAL-LEDHINE NAFEKU JEKULUNE LI’HWANIHIMUL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN ‘EHLIL-KITABI LE’IN ‘UHRIXHTUM LENEHRUXHENNE ME’AKUM WE LA NUTI’U FIKUM ‘EHEDÆN ‘EBEDÆN WE ‘IN KUTILTUM LENENSURENNEKUM WEL-LAHU JESH/HEDU ‘INNEHUM LEKADHIBUNE
  59,12,LE’IN ‘UHRIXHU LA JEHRUXHUNE ME’AHUM WE LE’IN KUTILU LA JENSURUNEHUM WE LE’IN NESERUHUM LEJUWELLUNNEL-’EDBARE THUMME LA JUNSERUNE
  59,13,LE’ENTUM ‘ESHEDDU REHBETEN FI SUDURIHIM MINEL-LAHI DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KAWMUN LA JEFKAHUNE
  59,14,LA JUKATILUNEKUM XHEMI’ÆN ‘ILLA FI KUREN MUHESSENETIN ‘EW MIN WERA’I XHUDURIN BE’SUHUM BEJNEHUM SHEDIDUN TEHSEBUHUM XHEMI’ÆN WE KULUBUHUM SHETTA DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM KAWMUN LA JA’KILUNE
  59,15,KEMETHELIL-LEDHINE MIN KABLIHIM KARIBÆN DHAKU WEBALE ‘EMRIHIM WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  59,16,KEMETHELI ESH-SHEJTANI ‘IDH KALE LIL’INSANI EKFUR FELEMMA KEFERE KALE ‘INNI BERI’UN MINKE ‘INNI ‘EHAFU ELLAHE REBBEL-’ALEMINE
  59,17,FEKANE ‘AKIBETEHUMA ‘ENNEHUMA FI EN-NARI HALIDEJNI FIHA WE DHELIKE XHEZA’U EDH-DHALIMINE
  59,18,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ETTEKU ELLAHE WE LTENDHUR NEFSUN MA KADDEMET LIGADIN WE ETTEKU ELLAHE ‘INNALL-LLAHE HABIRUN BIMA TA’MELUNE
  59,19,WE LA TEKUNU KALLEDHINE NESU ELLAHE FE’ENSAHUM ‘ENFUSEHUM ‘ULA’IKE HUMUL-FASIKUNE
  59,20,LA JESTEWI ‘ESHABU EN-NARI WE ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI ‘ESHABUL-XHENNETI HUMUL-FA’IZUNE
  59,21,LEW ‘ENZELNA HADHAL-KUR’ANE ‘ALA XHEBELIN LERE’EJTEHU HASHI’ÆN MUTESEDDI’ÆN MIN HASHJETI ELLAHI WE TILKEL-’EMTHALU NEDRIBUHA LILNNASI LE’ALLEHUM JETEFEKKERUNE
  59,22,HUWEL-LAHUL-LEDHI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE ‘ALIMUL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETI HUWE ER-REHMANU ER-REHIMU
  59,23,HUWEL-LAHUL-LEDHI LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWEL-MELIKUL-KUDDUSU ES-SELAMUL-MU’UMINUL-MUHEJMINUL-’AZIZUL-XHEBBARUL-MUTEKEBBIRU SUBHANEL-LAHI ‘AMMA JUSHRIKUNE
  59,24,HUWEL-LAHUL-HALIKUL-BARI’UL-MUSEWWIRU LEHUL-’ESMA’UL-HUSNA JUSEBBIHU LEHU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  60,1,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TETTEHIDHU ‘ADUWI WE ‘ADUWEKUM ‘EWLIJA’E TULKUNE ‘ILEJHIM BIL-MEWEDDETI WE KAD KEFERU BIMA XHA’EKUM MINEL-HEKKI JUHRIXHUNE ER-RESULE WE ‘IJAKUM ‘EN TU’UMINU BILLAHI RABBIKUM ‘IN KUNTUM HAREXHTUM XHIHADÆN FI SEBILI WE EBTIGA’E
  60,2,‘IN JETHKAFUKUM JEKUNU LEKUM ‘A’DA’EN WE JEBSUTU ‘ILEJKUM ‘EJDIJEHUM WE ‘ELSINETEHUM BIS-SU’I WE WEDDU LEW TEKFURUNE
  60,3,LEN TENFE’AKUM ‘ERHAMUKUM WE LA ‘EWLADUKUM JEWMEL-KIJAMETI JEFSILU BEJNEKUM WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  60,4,KAD KANET LEKUM ‘USWETUN HESENETUN FI ‘IBRAHIME WEL-LEDHINE ME’AHU ‘IDH KALU LIKAWMIHIM ‘INNA BURE’A’U MINKUM WE MIMMA TA’BUDUNE MIN DUNI ELLAHI KEFERNA BIKUM WE BEDA BEJNENA WE BEJNEKUMUL-’ADAWETU WEL-BEGDA’U ‘EBEDÆN HETTA TU’UMINU BILLAHI WEHDEHU ‘ILLA
  60,5,REBBENA LA TEXH’ALNA FITNETEN LILLEDHINE KEFERU WE EGFIR LENA REBBENA ‘INNEKE ‘ENTEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  60,6,LEKAD KANE LEKUM FIHIM ‘USWETUN HESENETUN LIMEN KANE JERXHU ELLAHE WEL-JEWMEL-’AHIRE WE MEN JETEWELLE FE’INNALL-LLAHE HUWEL-GANIJUL-HEMIDU
  60,7,‘ASALLAHU ‘EN JEXH’ALE BEJNEKUM WE BEJNEL-LEDHINE ‘ADEJTUM MINHUM MEWEDDETEN WEL-LAHU KADIRUN WEL-LAHU GAFURUN REHIMUN
  60,8,LA JENHAKUMU ELLAHU ‘ANIL-LEDHINE LEM JUKATILUKUM FI ED-DINI WE LEM JUHRIXHUKUM MIN DIJARIKUM ‘EN TEBERRUHUM WE TUKSITU ‘ILEJHIM ‘INNALL-LLAHE JUHIBBUL-MUKSITINE
  60,9,‘INNEMA JENHAKUMU ELLAHU ‘ANIL-LEDHINE KATELUKUM FI ED-DINI WE ‘EHREXHUKUM MIN DIJARIKUM WE DHAHERU ‘ALA ‘IHRAXHIKUM ‘EN TEWELLEWHUM WE MEN JETEWELLEHUM FE’ULA’IKE HUMU EDH-DHALIMUNE
  60,10,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA XHA’EKUMUL-MU’UMINATU MUHAXHIRATIN FAMTEHINUHUNNEL-LAHU ‘A’LEMU BI’IMANIHINNE FE’IN ‘ALIMTUMUHUNNE MU’UMINATIN FELA TERXHI’UHUNNE ‘ILAL-KUFFARI LA HUNNE HILLUN LEHUM WE LA HUM JEHILLUNE LEHUNNE WE ‘ATUHUM MA ‘ENFEKU WE LA
  60,11,WE ‘IN FATEKUM SHEJ’UN MIN ‘EZWAXHIKUM ‘ILAL-KUFFARI FA’AKABTUM FE’ATUL-LEDHINE DHEHEBET ‘EZWAXHUHUM MITHLE MA ‘ENFEKU WE ETTEKU ELLAHEL-LEDHI ‘ENTUM BIHI MU’UMINUNE
  60,12,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU ‘IDHA XHA’EKEL-MU’UMINATU JUBAJI’NEKE ‘ALA ‘EN LA JUSHRIKNE BILLAHI SHEJ’ÆN WE LA JESRIKNE WE LA JEZNINE WE LA JEKTULNE ‘EWLADEHUNNE WE LA JE’TINE BIBUHTANIN JEFTERINEHU BEJNE ‘EJDIHINNE WE ‘ERXHULIHINNE WE LA JA’SINEKE FI MA’RUFIN FE
  60,13,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TETEWELLEW KAWMÆN GADIBEL-LAHU ‘ALEJHIM KAD JE’ISU MINEL-’AHIRETI KEMA JE’ISEL-KUFFARU MIN ‘ESHABIL-KUBURI
  61,1,SEBBEHE LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  61,2,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘ÆMENU LIME TEKULUNE MA LA TEF’ALUNE
  61,3,KEBURE MEKTÆN ‘INDEL-LAHI ‘EN TEKULU MA LA TEF’ALUNE
  61,4,‘INNALL-LLAHE JUHIBBUL-LEDHINE JUKATILUNE FI SEBILIHI SEFFÆN KE’ENNEHUM BUNJANUN MERSUSUN
  61,5,WE ‘IDH KALE MUSA LIKAWMIHI JA KAWMI LIME TU’UDHUNENI WE KAD TA’LEMUNE ‘ENNI RESULU ELLAHI ‘ILEJKUM FELEMMA ZAGU ‘EZAGALLAHU KULUBEHUM WEL-LAHU LA JEHDIL-KAWMEL-FASIKINE
  61,6,WE ‘IDH KALE ‘ISA EBNU MERJEME JA BENI ‘ISRA’ILE ‘INNI RESULU ELLAHI ‘ILEJKUM MUSEDDIKÆN LIMA BEJNE JEDEJJE MINET-TEWRÆTI WE MUBESHSHIRÆN BIRESULIN JE’TI MIN BA’DI ESMUHU ‘EHMEDU FELEMMA XHA’EHUM BIL-BEJJINATI KALU HADHA SIHRUN MUBINUN
  61,7,WE MEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHIL-KEDHIBE WE HUWE JUD’A ‘ILAL-’ISLAMI WEL-LAHU LA JEHDIL-KAWME EDH-DHALIMINE
  61,8,JURIDUNE LIJUTFI’U NUREL-LAHI BI’EFWAHIHIM WEL-LAHU MUTIMMU NURIHI WE LEW KERIHEL-KAFIRUNE
  61,9,HUWEL-LEDHI ‘ERSELE RESULEHU BIL-HUDA WE DINIL-HEKKI LIJUDHHIREHU ‘ALA ED-DINI KULLIHI WE LEW KERIHEL-MUSHRIKUNE
  61,10,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘ÆMENU HEL ‘EDULLUKUM ‘ALA TIXHARETIN TUNXHIKUM MIN ‘ADHABIN ‘ELIMIN
  61,11,TU’UMINUNE BILLAHI WE RESULIHI WE TUXHAHIDUNE FI SEBILI ELLAHI BI’EMWALIKUM WE ‘ENFUSIKUM DHALIKUM HAJRUN LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  61,12,JEGFIR LEKUM DHUNUBEKUM WE JUDHILKUM XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU WE MESAKINE TEJJIBETEN FI XHENNATI ‘ADNIN DHALIKEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  61,13,WE ‘UHRA TUHIBBUNEHA NESRUN MINEL-LAHI WE FETHUN KARIBUN WE BESHSHIRIL-MU’UMININE
  61,14,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘ÆMENU KUNW ‘ENSAREL-LAHI KEMA KALE ‘ISA EBNU MERJEME LILHEWARIJINE MEN ‘ENSARI ‘ILA ELLAHI KALEL-HEWARIJUNE NEHNU ‘ENSARU ELLAHI FE’ÆMENET TA’IFETUN MIN BENI ‘ISRA’ILE WE KEFERET TA’IFETUN FE’EJJEDNAL-LEDHINE ‘ÆMENU ‘ALA ‘ADUWIHIM FE’
  62,1,JUSEBBIHU LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDIL-MELIKIL-KUDDUSIL-’AZIZIL-HEKIMI
  62,2,HUWEL-LEDHI BE’ATHE FIL-’UMMIJINE RESULÆN MINHUM JETLU ‘ALEJHIM ‘AJATIHI WE JUZEKKIHIM WE JU’ALLIMUHUMUL-KITABE WEL-HIKMETE WE ‘IN KANU MIN KABLU LEFI DELALIN MUBININ
  62,3,WE ‘AHARINE MINHUM LEMMA JELHEKU BIHIM WE HUWEL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  62,4,DHALIKE FEDLU ELLAHI JU’UTIHI MEN JESHA’U WEL-LAHU DHUL-FEDLIL-’ADHIMI
  62,5,METHELUL-LEDHINE HUMMILUT-TEWRÆTE THUMME LEM JEHMILUHA KEMETHELIL-HIMARI JEHMILU ‘ESFARÆN BI’SE METHELUL-KAWMIL-LEDHINE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATI ELLAHI WEL-LAHU LA JEHDIL-KAWME EDH-DHALIMINE
  62,6,KUL JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE HADU ‘IN ZE’AMTUM ‘ENNEKUM ‘EWLIJA ‘U LILLAHI MIN DUNI EN-NASI FETEMENNEWL-MEWTE ‘IN KUNTUM SADIKINE
  62,7,WE LA JETEMENNEWNEHU ‘EBEDÆN BIMA KADDEMET ‘EJDIHIM WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN BIDH-DHALIMINE
  62,8,KUL ‘INNEL-MEWTEL-LEDHI TEFIRRUNE MINHU FE’INNEHU MULAKIKUM THUMME TUREDDUNE ‘ILA ‘ALIMIL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETI FEJUNEBBI’UKUM BIMA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  62,9,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘IDHA NUDI LILSSELÆTI MIN JEWMIL-XHUMU’ATI FAS’AW ‘ILA DHIKRI ELLAHI WE DHERUL-BEJ’A DHALIKUM HAJRUN LEKUM ‘IN KUNTUM TA’LEMUNE
  62,10,FE’IDHA KUDIJETI ES-SELÆTU FANTESHIRU FIL-’ERDI WE EBTEGU MIN FEDLI ELLAHI WE EDHKURU ELLAHE KETHIRÆN LE’ALLEKUM TUFLIHUNE
  62,11,WE ‘IDHA RE’EW TIXHARETEN ‘EW LEHWEN ENFEDDU ‘ILEJHA WE TEREKUKE KA’IMÆN KUL MA ‘INDEL-LAHI HAJRUN MINEL-LEHWI WE MINET-TIXHARETI WEL-LAHU HAJRU ER-RAZIKINE
  63,1,‘IDHA XHA’EKEL-MUNAFIKUNE KALU NESH/HEDU ‘INNEKE LERESULU ELLAHI WEL-LAHU JA’LEMU ‘INNEKE LERESULUHU WEL-LAHU JESH/HEDU ‘INNEL-MUNAFIKINE LEKADHIBUNE
  63,2,ETTEHADHU ‘EJMANEHUM XHUNNETEN FESEDDU ‘AN SEBILI ELLAHI ‘INNEHUM SA’E MA KANU JA’MELUNE
  63,3,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHUM ‘AMENU THUMME KEFERU FETUBI’A ‘ALA KULUBIHIM FEHUM LA JEFKAHUNE
  63,4,WE ‘IDHA RE’EJTEHUM TU’XHIBUKE ‘EXHSAMUHUM WE ‘IN JEKULU TESMA’ LIKAWLIHIM KE’ENNEHUM HUSHUBUN MUSENNEDETUN JEHSEBUNE KULLE SEJHETIN ‘ALEJHIM HUMUL-’ADUWU FAHDHERHUM KATELEHUMU ELLAHU ‘ENNA JU’UFEKUNE
  63,5,WE ‘IDHA KILE LEHUM TA’ALEW JESTEGFIR LEKUM RESULU ELLAHI LEWWEW RU’USEHUM WE RE’EJTEHUM JESUDDUNE WE HUM MUSTEKBIRUNE
  63,6,SEWA’UN ‘ALEJHIM ‘ASTEGFERTE LEHUM ‘EM LEM TESTEGFIR LEHUM LEN JEGFIREL-LAHU LEHUM ‘INNALL-LLAHE LA JEHDIL-KAWMEL-FASIKINE
  63,7,HUMUL-LEDHINE JEKULUNE LA TUNFIKU ‘ALA MEN ‘INDE RESULI ELLAHI HETTA JENFEDDU WE LILLEHI HAZA’INU ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE LEKINNEL-MUNAFIKINE LA JEFKAHUNE
  63,8,JEKULUNE LE’IN REXHA’NA ‘ILAL-MEDINETI LEJUHRIXHENNEL-’E’AZZU MINHAL-’EDHELLE WE LILLEHIL-’IZZETU WE LIRESULIHI WE LILMU’UMININE WE LEKINNEL-MUNAFIKINE LA JA’LEMUNE
  63,9,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU LA TULHIKUM ‘EMWALUKUM WE LA ‘EWLADUKUM ‘AN DHIKRI ELLAHI WE MEN JEF’AL DHALIKE FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-HASIRUNE
  63,10,WE ‘ENFIKU MIN MA REZEKNAKUM MIN KABLI ‘EN JE’TIJE ‘EHEDEKUMUL-MEWTU FEJEKULE RABBI LEWLA ‘EHHARTENI ‘ILA ‘EXHELIN KARIBIN FE’ESSEDDEKA WE ‘EKUN MINE ES-SALIHINE
  63,11,WE LEN JU’UEHHIREL-LAHU NEFSÆN ‘IDHA XHA’E ‘EXHELUHA WEL-LAHU HABIRUN BIMA TA’MELUNE
  64,1,JUSEBBIHU LILLAHI MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WE MA FIL-’ERDI LEHUL-MULKU WE LEHUL-HEMDU WE HUWE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN
  64,2,HUWEL-LEDHI HALEKAKUM FEMINKUM KAFIRUN WE MINKUM MU’UMINUN WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE BESIRUN
  64,3,HALEKA ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDE BIL-HEKKI WE SEWWEREKUM FE’EHSENE SUWEREKUM WE ‘ILEJHIL-MESIRU
  64,4,JA’LEMU MA FI ES-SEMAWATI WEL-’ERDI WE JA’LEMU MA TUSIRRUNE WE MA TU’LINUNE WEL-LAHU ‘ALIMUN BIDHATI ES-SUDURI
  64,5,‘ELEM JE’TIKUM NEBE’UL-LEDHINE KEFERU MIN KABLU FEDHAKU WEBALE ‘EMRIHIM WE LEHUM ‘ADHABUN ‘ELIMUN
  64,6,DHALIKE BI’ENNEHU KANET TE’TIHIM RUSULUHUM BIL-BEJJINATI FEKALU ‘EBESHERUN JEHDUNENA FEKEFERU WE TEWELLEW WE ESTEGNALLAHU WEL-LAHU GANIJUN HEMIDUN
  64,7,ZE’AMEL-LEDHINE KEFERU ‘EN LEN JUB’ATHU KUL BELA WE RABBI LETUB’ATHUNNE THUMME LETUNEBBE’UUNNE BIMA ‘AMILTUM WE DHELIKE ‘ALA ELLAHI JESIRUN
  64,8,FE’AMINU BILLAHI WE RESULIHI WE EN-NURIL-LEDHI ‘ENZELNA WEL-LAHU BIMA TA’MELUNE HABIRUN
  64,9,JEWME JEXHMA’UKUM LIJEWMIL-XHEM’I DHALIKE JEWMUT-TEGABUNI WE MEN JU’UMIN BILLAHI WE JA’MEL SALIHÆN JUKEFFIR ‘ANHU SEJJI’ATIHI WE JUDHILHU XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA ‘EBEDÆN DHALIKEL-FEWZUL-’ADHIMU
  64,10,WEL-LEDHINE KEFERU WE KEDHDHEBU BI’AJATINA ‘ULA’IKE ‘ESHABU EN-NARI HALIDINE FIHA WE BI’SEL-MESIRU
  64,11,MA ‘ESABE MIN MUSIBETIN ‘ILLA BI’IDHNI ELLAHI WE MEN JU’UMIN BILLAHI JEHDI KALBEHU WEL-LAHU BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ALIMUN
  64,12,WE ‘ETI’U ELLAHE WE ‘ETI’U ER-RESULE FE’IN TEWELLEJTUM FE’INNEMA ‘ALA RESULINAL-BELAGUL-MUBINU
  64,13,ELLAHU LA ‘ILAHE ‘ILLA HUWE WE ‘ALA ELLAHI FELJETEWEKKELIL-MU’UMINUNE
  64,14,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ‘INNE MIN ‘EZWAXHIKUM WE ‘EWLADIKUM ‘ADUWÆN LEKUM FAHDHERUHUM WE ‘IN TA’FU WE TESFEHU WE TEGFIRU FE’INNALL-LLAHE GAFURUN REHIMUN
  64,15,‘INNEMA ‘EMWALUKUM WE ‘EWLADUKUM FITNETUN WEL-LAHU ‘INDEHU ‘EXHRUN ‘ADHIMUN
  64,16,FATTEKU ELLAHE MA ESTETA’TUM WE ESMA’U WE ‘ETI’U WE ‘ENFIKU HAJRÆN LI’NFUSIKUM WE MEN JUKA SHUHHE NEFSIHI FE’ULA’IKE HUMUL-MUFLIHUNE
  64,17,‘IN TUKRIDU ELLAHE KARDÆN HESENÆN JUDA’IFHU LEKUM WE JEGFIR LEKUM WEL-LAHU SHEKURUN HELIMUN
  64,18,‘ALIMUL-GAJBI WE ESH-SHEHADETIL-’AZIZUL-HEKIMU
  65,1,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU ‘IDHA TELLEKTUMU EN-NISA’ FETELLIKUHUNNE LI’IDDETIHINNE WE ‘EHSUL-’IDDETE WE ETTEKU ELLAHE REBBEKUM LA TUHRIXHUHUNNE MIN BUJUTIHINNE WE LA JEHRUXHNE ‘ILLA ‘EN JE’TINE BIFAHISHETIN MUBEJJINETIN WE TILKE HUDUDU ELLAHI WE MEN JETE’ADDE H
  65,2,FE’IDHA BELEGNE ‘EXHELEHUNNE FE’EMSIKUHUNNE BIMA’RUFIN ‘EW FARIKUHUNNE BIMA’RUFIN WE ‘ESH/HIDU DHEWEJ ‘ADLIN MINKUM WE ‘EKIMU ESH-SHEHADETE LILLAHI DHALIKUM JU’ADHU BIHI MEN KANE JU’UMINU BILLAHI WEL-JEWMIL-’AHIRI WE MEN JETTEKI ELLAHE JEXH’AL LEHU MEHREX
  65,3,WE JERZUKHU MIN HEJTHU LA JEHTESIBU WE MEN JETEWEKKEL ‘ALA ELLAHI FEHUWE HESBUHU ‘INNALL-LLAHE BALIGU ‘EMRIHI KAD XHE’ALEL-LAHU LIKULLI SHEJ’IN KADRÆN
  65,4,WEL-LA’I JE’ISNE MINEL-MEHIDI MIN NISA’IKUM ‘INI ERTEBTUM FA’IDDETUHUNNE THELATHETU ‘ESH/HURIN WEL-LA’I LEM JEHIDNE WE ‘ULATUL-’EHMALI ‘EXHELUHUNNE ‘EN JEDA’NE HEMLEHUNNE WE MEN JETTEKI ELLAHE JEXH’AL LEHU MIN ‘EMRIHI JUSRÆN
  65,5,DHALIKE ‘EMRU ELLAHI ‘ENZELEHU ‘ILEJKUM WE MEN JETTEKI ELLAHE JUKEFFIR ‘ANHU SEJJI’ATIHI WE JU’DHIM LEHU ‘EXHRÆN
  65,6,‘ESKINUHUNNE MIN HEJTHU SEKENTUM MIN WUXHDIKUM WE LA TUDARRUHUNNE LITUDEJJIKU ‘ALEJHINNE WE ‘IN KUNNE ‘ULATI HEMLIN FE’ENFIKU ‘ALEJHINNE HETTA JEDA’NE HEMLEHUNNE FE’IN ‘ERDA’NE LEKUM FE’ATUHUNNE ‘UXHUREHUNNE WE ‘TEMIRU BEJNEKUM BIMA’RUFIN WE ‘IN TA’ASERTU
  65,7,LIJUNFIK DHU SE’ATIN MIN SE’ATIHI WE MEN KUDIRE ‘ALEJHI RIZKUHU FELJUNFIK MIMMA ‘ATAHU ELLAHU LA JUKELLIFU ELLAHU NEFSÆN ‘ILLA MA ‘ATAHA SEJEXH’ALU ELLAHU BA’DE ‘USRIN JUSRÆN
  65,8,WE KE’EJJIN MIN KARJETIN ‘ATET ‘AN ‘EMRI RABBIHA WE RUSULIHI FEHASEBNAHA HISABÆN SHEDIDÆN WE ‘ADHDHEBNAHA ‘ADHABÆN NUKRÆN
  65,9,FEDHAKAT WEBALE ‘EMRIHA WE KANE ‘AKIBETU ‘EMRIHA HUSRÆN
  65,10,‘E’ADDEL-LAHU LEHUM ‘ADHABÆN SHEDIDÆN FE ETTEKU ELLAHE JA ‘ULIL-’ELBABIL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU KAD ‘ENZELEL-LAHU ‘ILEJKUM DHIKRÆN
  65,11,RESULÆN JETLU ‘ALEJKUM ‘AJATI ELLAHI MUBEJJINATIN LIJUHRIXHEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU WE ‘AMILU ES-SALIHATI MINE EDH-DHULUMATI ‘ILA EN-NURI WE MEN JU’UMIN BILLAHI WE JA’MEL SALIHÆN JUDHILHU XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU HALIDINE FIHA ‘EBEDÆN KAD ‘EHSENEL-L
  65,12,ELLAHUL-LEDHI HALEKA SEB’A SEMAWATIN WE MINEL-’ERDI MITHLEHUNNE JETENEZZELUL-’EMRU BEJNEHUNNE LITA’LEMU ‘ENNEL-LAHE ‘ALA KULLI SHEJ’IN KADIRUN WE ‘ENNEL-LAHE KAD ‘EHATE BIKULLI SHEJ’IN ‘ILMÆN
  66,1,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU LIME TUHERRIMU MA ‘EHELLEL-LAHU LEKE TEBTEGI MERDÆTE ‘EZWAXHIKE WEL-LAHU GAFURUN REHIMUN
  66,2,KAD FEREDEL-LAHU LEKUM TEHILLETE ‘EJMANIKUM WEL-LAHU MEWLAKUM WE HUWEL-’ALIMUL-HEKIMU
  66,3,WE ‘IDH ‘ESERRE EN-NEBIJU ‘ILA BA’DI ‘EZWAXHIHI HEDITHÆN FELEMMA NEBBE’ET BIHI WE ‘EDHHEREHU ELLAHU ‘ALEJHI ‘ARREFE BA’DEHU WE ‘A’REDE ‘AN BA’DIN FELEMMA NEBBE’EHA BIHI KALET MEN ‘ENBE’EKE HADHA KALE NEBBE’ENIJEL-’ALIMUL-HABIRU
  66,4,‘IN TETUBA ‘ILA ELLAHI FEKAD SEGAT KULUBUKUMA WE ‘IN TEDHAHERA ‘ALEJHI FE’INNALL-LLAHE HUWE MEWLAHU WE XHIBRILU WE SALIHUL-MU’UMININE WEL-MELA’IKETU BA’DE DHALIKE DHEHIRUN
  66,5,‘ASA REBBUHU ‘IN TELLEKAKUNNE ‘EN JUBDILEHU ‘EZWAXHÆN HAJRÆN MINKUNNE MUSLIMATIN MU’UMINATIN KANITATIN TA’IBATIN ‘ABIDATIN SA’IHATIN THEJJIBATIN WE ‘EBKARÆN
  66,6,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU KU ‘ENFUSEKUM WE ‘EHLIKUM NARÆN WEKUDUHA EN-NASU WEL-HIXHARETU ‘ALEJHA MELA’IKETUN GILADHUN SHIDADUN LA JA’SUNEL-LAHE MA ‘EMEREHUM WE JEF’ALUNE MA JU’UMERUNE
  66,7,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE KEFERU LA TA’TEDHIRUL-JEWME ‘INNEMA TUXHZEWNE MA KUNTUM TA’MELUNE
  66,8,JA ‘EJJUHAL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU TUBU ‘ILA ELLAHI TEWBETEN NESUHÆN ‘ASA REBBUKUM ‘EN JUKEFFIRE ‘ANKUM SEJJI’ATIKUM WE JUDHILEKUM XHENNATIN TEXHRI MIN TEHTIHAL-’ENHARU JEWME LA JUHZI ELLAHU EN-NEBIJE WEL-LEDHINE ‘AMENU ME’AHU NURUHUM JES’A BEJNE ‘EJDIHIM WE BI’E
  66,9,JA ‘EJJUHA EN-NEBIJU XHAHIDIL-KUFFARE WEL-MUNAFIKINE WE EGLUDH ‘ALEJHIM WE ME’WAHUM XHEHENNEMU WE BI’SEL-MESIRU
  66,10,DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN LILLEDHINE KEFERU EIMRE’ETE NUHIN WE EIMRE’ETE LUTIN KANETA TEHTE ‘ABDEJNI MIN ‘IBADINA SALIHEJNI FEHANETAHUMA FELEM JUGNIJA ‘ANHUMA MINEL-LAHI SHEJ’ÆN WE KILE EDHULA EN-NARE ME’A ED-DAHILINE
  66,11,WE DEREBEL-LAHU METHELÆN LILLEDHINE ‘AMENU EIMRE’ETE FIR’AWNE ‘IDH KALET RABBI EBNI LI ‘INDEKE BEJTÆN FIL-XHENNETI WE NEXHXHINI MIN FIR’AWNE WE ‘AMELIHI WE NEXHXHINI MINEL-KAWMI EDH-DHALIMINE
  66,12,WE MERJEME EBNETE ‘IMRANEL-LETI ‘EHSENET FERXHEHA FENEFEHNA FIHI MIN RUHINA WE SEDDEKAT BIKELIMATI RABBIHA WE KUTUBIHI WE KANET MINEL-KANITINE